      <i class="fa-solid fa-paper-plane"></i>
      <input type="search" placeholder="Send AI instruction..." />
    </div>

  </div>

  <p>Conversational AI workspace with floating messages, assistant prompts, and interactive commands.</p>

  <div class="card-actions">
    <button>Preview</button>
    <button>Use pattern</button>
  </div>
</article>
